problem_statement:
`AdaptiveByteBufAllocator.usedHeapMemory` does not include fallback buffers
The `usedHeapMemory` metric does not include fallback buffers. Test case:

```java
    @Test
    public void testUsedHeapMemoryHuge() {
        AdaptiveByteBufAllocator allocator =  newAllocator(true);
        ByteBufAllocatorMetric metric = allocator.metric();
        assertEquals(0, metric.usedHeapMemory());
        int size = 32 * 1024 * 1024;
        ByteBuf buffer = allocator.heapBuffer(size, size);
        assertEquals(size, metric.usedHeapMemory());
        buffer.release();
    }
```

